{"tid":2078324,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山西平順落暴雨冰雹 部分縣城水浸","createTime":"2020-06-25T03:24:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T06:29:34.000Z","uid":19552,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c268feaec1549bf93cf4adc05abe632f74115dcd","tid":2078324,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:24:58.000Z","msg":"山西中部長治市多處地區，昨日下午出現強對流天氣，其中平順縣於於傍晚時份落暴雨和冰雹，雨量到晚上8時已達到115.3毫米，導致平順縣城及部分鄉鎮發生內澇，截至晚上10時半，雨勢才結束。<br />\n<br />\n山西省氣象台預計今日早上，山西大部分地區將出現雷暴大風、冰雹或短暫強降雨等強對流天氣，要求有關單位和人員做好防範暴雨、防雷、防大風準備工作，氣象部門做好人工防雹作業；應檢查城市、農田排水系統，做好排澇準備和對山洪、滑坡、泥石流等災害的防禦準備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1804234/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%B9%B3%E9%A0%86%E8%90%BD%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E5%86%B0%E9%9B%B9-%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%B8%A3%E5%9F%8E%E6%B0%B4%E6%B5%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1804234%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E9%25A0%2586%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%259A%25B4%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2586%25B0%25E9%259B%25B9-%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25B8%25A3%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B5%25B8&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2Qff%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=23e9cd55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1804234%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E9%25A0%2586%25E8%2590%25BD%25E6%259A%25B4%25E9%259B%25A8%25E5%2586%25B0%25E9%259B%25B9-%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586%25E7%25B8%25A3%25E5%259F%258E%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B5%25B8&h=f73fdd1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/chi/1804234/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E5%B1%B1%E8%A5%BF%E5%B9%B3%E9%A0%86%E8%90%BD%E6%9A%B4%E9%9B%A8%E5%86%B0%E9%9B%B9-%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E7%B8%A3%E5%9F%8E%E6%B0%B4%E6%B5%B8</a>"},{"